snippet.title: Underworld Re: Card | ON Steam Game
snippet.description:
Japanese Anime Style X Roguelike Deck-building CCGReborn into Underworld As A Hero!"Underworld Re: Card" is a game that combines deck-building and Rogue-like elements. Players are reborn into various races to fight and explore in the fantasy world. 

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2101180/Underworld_Re_Card/
